        "title": "Small pet carrier",
        "text": "Neutral and sturdy pet carrier for your sad beige mom. There are several events on all sides, including the top to make your pet comfortable. Also, zippers on the front, back and top, for convenience. It also comes with a detachable strap to where cross body or around the shoulders. My only gripe is that the handles don't clip together properly. It took a lot of strength to just get the buttons snapped on, and the handle doesn't fold correctly; for that I took off a star. Other than that, I highly recommend this pet carrier for your small dog or cat. Current value is $54.99, which does sound a little steep, but it does look like good quality faux leather.",
